Build instructions for libsomanetwork. 

NOTE: In general, you should use one of the pre-built debs for most
Soma software, including this library.

BUILD REQUIREMENTS:
autotools / automake
Boost 1.34.1

These packages are available from the Ubuntu 8.04
package archive.

Typically, building can be accomplished with : 

./autogen.sh
./configure
make
sudo make install


To run the unit tests, 
make check
